  <entry>
    <title>BD环境部署04-HBase 0.98.24环境搭建</title>
    <link href="/2022/01/21/BD%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B204-HBase%200.98.24%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <url>/2022/01/21/BD%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B204-HBase%200.98.24%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li>下载hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2-bin.tar.gz并上传到/usr/local/src目录下，然后解压。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># cd /usr/local/src/</span><br>[root@master src]<span class="hljs-comment"># ls | grep hb</span><br>hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2-bin.tar.gz<br>[root@master src]<span class="hljs-comment"># tar -zxvf hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2-bin.tar.gz </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>进入hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2/conf目录，编辑regionservers文件。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master src]<span class="hljs-comment"># cd hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2/conf/</span><br>[root@master conf]<span class="hljs-comment"># vim regionservers </span><br>[root@master conf]<span class="hljs-comment"># cat regionservers </span><br>master<br>slave1<br>slave2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>编辑hbase-env.sh。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master conf]<span class="hljs-comment"># vim hbase-env.sh </span><br>[root@master conf]<span class="hljs-comment"># tail -n 2 hbase-env.sh </span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> JAVA_HOME=/usr/local/src/jdk1.8.0_212<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> CLASSPATH=.:<span class="hljs-variable">$CLASSPATH</span>:<span class="hljs-variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>编辑hbase-site.xml配置文件。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master conf]<span class="hljs-comment"># vim hbase-site.xml</span><br>[root@master conf]<span class="hljs-comment"># cat hbase-site.xml</span><br>&lt;configuration&gt;<br>    &lt;property&gt;<br>        &lt;name&gt;hbase.tmp.dir&lt;/name&gt;<br>        &lt;value&gt;/var/hbase&lt;/value&gt;<br>    &lt;/property&gt;<br><br>    &lt;property&gt;<br>        &lt;name&gt;hbase.rootdir&lt;/name&gt;<br>        &lt;value&gt;hdfs://master:9000/hbase&lt;/value&gt;<br>    &lt;/property&gt;<br><br>    &lt;property&gt;<br>        &lt;name&gt;hbase.cluster.distributed&lt;/name&gt;<br>        &lt;value&gt;<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>&lt;/value&gt;<br>    &lt;/property&gt;<br><br>    &lt;property&gt;<br>        &lt;name&gt;hbase.zookeeper.quorum&lt;/name&gt;<br>        &lt;value&gt;master,slave1,slave2&lt;/value&gt;<br>    &lt;/property&gt;<br><br>    &lt;property&gt;<br>        &lt;name&gt;hbase.zookeeper.property.dataDir&lt;/name&gt;<br>        &lt;value&gt;/usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2/zookeeper&lt;/value&gt;<br>    &lt;/property&gt;<br><br>    &lt;property&gt;<br>        &lt;name&gt;hbase.master.info.port&lt;/name&gt;<br>        &lt;value&gt;60010&lt;/value&gt;<br>    &lt;/property&gt; <br>&lt;/configuration&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>创建目录。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># cd /usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2</span><br>[root@master hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2]<span class="hljs-comment"># mkdir logs</span><br>[root@master hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2]<span class="hljs-comment"># mkdir zookeeper</span><br>[root@master hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2]<span class="hljs-comment"># mkdir -p /var/hbase</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>同步HBase到slave1和slave2。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># scp -r /usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2 root@slave1:/usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2</span><br>[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># scp -r /usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2 root@slave2:/usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>配置环境变量。（master、slave1、slave2）</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># vim /etc/profile</span><br>[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># tail -n 5 /etc/profile</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">## HBASE_HOME</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> HBASE_HOME=/usr/local/src/hbase-0.98.24-hadoop2<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> HBASE_CLASSPATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$HBASE_HOME</span>/conf<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> HBASE_LOG_DIR=<span class="hljs-variable">$HBASE_HOME</span>/logs<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span>:<span class="hljs-variable">$HBASE_HOME</span>/bin<br>[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># source /etc/profile</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>启动Hadoop。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># cd $HADOOP_HOME </span><br>[root@master hadoop-2.8.2]<span class="hljs-comment"># sbin/start-all.sh </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>启动集群。</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># start-hbase.sh</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>查看状态。</p><ul><li>master：HMaster、HRegionServer、HQuorumPeer</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@master ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># jps</span><br>1552 NameNode<br>2644 HRegionServer<br>1929 ResourceManager<br>2938 Jps<br>2491 HMaster<br>1758 SecondaryNameNode<br>2430 HQuorumPeer<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>slave1：HRegionServer、HQuorumPeer</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@slave1 ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># jps</span><br>1459 HQuorumPeer<br>1539 HRegionServer<br>1236 NodeManager<br>1161 DataNode<br>1707 Jps<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>slave2：HRegionServer、HQuorumPeer</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">[root@slave2 ~]<span class="hljs-comment"># jps</span><br>1236 NodeManager<br>1157 DataNode<br>1542 HRegionServer<br>1721 Jps<br>1455 HQuorumPeer<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>监控页面：<a href="http://192.168.10.201:60010/master-status">http://192.168.10.201:60010/master-status</a></p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
